Thing	What it means
Redis still required	Bull queues need Redis running on the target machine. The exe does not embed Redis — users must install it separately or point REDIS_HOST/REDIS_PORT env vars at a hosted Redis.
PubNub	Works fine — it's a cloud API over HTTPS, nothing native.
Native .node files	If any dependency has a prebuilt native addon (.node file), pkg copies it next to the exe automatically but it must stay in the same folder. Run the exe from its directory or set NODE_PATH.
Node version in targets	@yao-pkg/pkg currently supports up to Node 22. Your dev machine runs Node 24 but the compiled JS is fully compatible.
PORT env var	Set it before running: PORT=3001 ./GGL-DS-MIST-linux on Linux/macOS, or $env:PORT=3001; .\GGL-DS-MIST-win.exe in PowerShell.